



Sir
Decr 12th 1774.



I will endeavour to attend the Committee, on Wednesday, agreeable to your notice.1 No conveyance is like to happen, that I know of, from hence to Colo. Mason previous to the meeting; otherwise I should not fail to give him notice & request his attendanceIt now rests upon you to do it. I am Sir Yr Most Obedt Servt

Go: Washington

